                                                                        Before Insert - Examples
                                                                        -----------------------
Q) Write a Trigger on the Account object to make Phone field mandatory?
trigger AccountTrigger on Account (before insert) {
    for(Account acc : Trigger.New){
        if(acc.Phone == Null){
            acc.addError('Phone number is Mandatory for every new record creation');
        }
    }
}
(Or)
trigger AccountTrigger on Account (before insert) {
    List<Account> lstacc = Trigger.New;
    for(Account acc : lstacc){
        if(acc.Phone == Null){
            acc.phone.addError('Phone number is Mandatory for every new record creation');
        }
    }
}
-------------------
Q) Write a Trigger on the Account object, If Phone is not Null and Fax is Null then get the Phone value under Fax field?
trigger AccountTrigger2 on Account (before insert) {
    for(Account acc:Trigger.new){
        if(acc.Phone != Null && acc.Fax== Null){
            acc.fax = acc.phone;
        }
    }
}
-------------------
